    <stitle>International&#174; T 444E Diesel Engine Service, Model Year 1994 - 1998 - TURBOCHARGER - Assembly</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>Assembly</title>
        <svcproc graphiccount="1">
            <title>Install Turbocharger Pedestal (Standard Torque Model)</title>
            <figure id="f1200231" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic filename="../figeg2/EG2500.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="328px"
                         scalefitheight="472px" box="yes"/>
                <caption>Assembling the Turbocharger to the Pedestal</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger Pedestal</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Pedestal Mounting Bolts</callout1>
                    <callout1 type="arabic">Turbocharger</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">If removed, install the solenoid valve and tighten the mounting bolt.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Lubricate and install two new oil O-rings onto the pedestal.</para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Apply Never-Seez&#8482; to the threads of the four mounting bolts. Install and tighten
                    the mounting bolts to the special torque value.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
